column3: An aether compass? Aye, one of those turned up the other day. Can't rightly say where it came from, but if you want it, it's yours.
Eh? Aether compass? Don't think I've seen anything like that lying around. Sorry I couldn't be of more help.
Misplaced an aether compass, did you? Well, you're in luck. Got one right here that someone was kind enough to hand over instead of selling to the sutlers. Try not to lose it again, eh?
Looking for an aether compass? 'Fraid you'll find none here. I'll keep an eye out in case one turns up, though.
Aether compasses? Why yes, I have distributed a fair few in the course of my duties.
I believe this is the one you are searching for, though I would encourage you to take better care of it from now on. These things do not grow on trees, you know!
Unfortunately, I have not seen any like the one you describe. I shall keep an eye out for it, though.
